import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import { Row,Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';
import "./FormClients.css"
import { useState } from 'react';

const FormClients = () => {
  const [client, setClient] = useState({
    CompanyName:"",
    CompanyStreet:"",
    CompanyCity:"",
    CompanyState:"",
    CompanyZip:"",
    Gsttreatment:"",
    Vat:"",
    Phone:"",
    Mobile:"",
    WebsiteLink:"",
    Tags:"",

  });
  

  return (
    <>
    <Container fluid className='backgroundd'>
      <Row className='mt-5 pt-5'>
        <Col lg={5}>
        <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Name" id="CompanyName" onChange={(e)=>state.CompanyName(e.target.value)} />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    <Row className='my-5'>
      <Col lg={5}>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{span: 4}}>
            <Form.Label htmlFor="Company Adresse">Company Adresse:</Form.Label>
            </Col>
          <Col >
            <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Street"  id="Company Adresse" onChange={(e)=>setClient.CompanyAdresse(e.target.value)} />
            </Col>
            </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{ span: 8, offset: 4 }}>
            <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Street2.." id="Company Street" onChange={(e)=>setClient.CompanyStreet(e.target.value)} />
            </Col>
            </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{ span: 8, offset: 4 }}>
          <Row className='mb-2'>
            <Col>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="City" id="Company City" onChange={(e)=>setClient.CompanyCity(e.target.value)} />
              </Col>
            <Col>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="State" id="Company State" onChange={(e)=>setClient.CompanyState(e.target.value)} />
              </Col>
            <Col>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="ZIP" id="Company ZIP" onChange={(e)=>setClient.CompanyZip(e.target.value)} />
              </Col>
              </Row>
            </Col>
          <Col lg={{ span: 8, offset: 4 }}>
            <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Country" onChange={(e)=>setClient.CompanyCountry(e.target.value)} />
            </Col>
          </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{span: 4}}><Form.Label htmlFor="GST treatment">GST treatment:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" id='GST treatment' onChange={(e)=>setClient.Gsttreatment(e.target.value)}/></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{span: 4}}><Form.Label htmlFor="VAT">VAT:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="e.g BE3546843468" id='VAT' onChange={(e)=>setClient.Vat(e.target.value)} /></Col>
        </Row> 
      </Col>
      <Col lg={6}>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{offset: 2}}><Form.Label htmlFor="Phone">Phone:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col lg={{span: 8}}><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" id="Phone" onChange={(e)=>setClient.Phone(e.target.value)} /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{offset: 2}}><Form.Label htmlFor="Mobile">Mobile:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col lg={{span: 8}}><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" id="Mobile" onChange={(e)=>setClient.Mobile(e.target.value)} /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{offset: 2}}><Form.Label htmlFor="Email">Email:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col lg={{span: 8}}><Form.Control size="sm" type="text"id="Email" onChange={(e)=>setClient.Email(e.target.value)} /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{offset: 2}}><Form.Label htmlFor="Website Link">Website Link:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col lg={{span: 8}}><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="e.g https //www.google.com" id="Website Link" onChange={(e)=>setClient.WebsiteLink(e.target.value)} /></Col>
        </Row>
        <Row className='mb-2'>
          <Col lg={{offset: 2 }}><Form.Label htmlFor="Tags">Tags:</Form.Label></Col>
          <Col lg={{span: 8}}><Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="tags..." id="Tags" onChange={(e)=>setClient.Ctags(e.target.value)} /></Col>
        </Row>
      </Col>
      </Row>
      </Container>

    </>
  );
}

export default FormClients;
